{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were trying to get the prisoners to calm down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- and I didn't know how they-- till later, how they did this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They got the leadership of-- and there was-- there was an inter-- a structure just like there was in every camp-- to take over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and these were usually Jewish rabbis or people like that, and calm, calm down and get an order.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and go back to your barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we'll sort-- we're going to bring food, and, you know, that kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is what the inmates were finally-- what finally happened was that the-- the leadership of the camp, which were chosen by the inmates-- and there some-- there were some priests, a few priests, quite a few rabbis in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And kill-- they'd killed a couple hundred priests already from Poland, polish priests.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, I remember things subsiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said-- the driver.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wish I could think of his name now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's dead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm in touch with his wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyhow he said, you've got to see the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, the gas chamber?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They got-- and I hadn't even heard about the gas chambers yet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, yeah and there's a crematorium part of the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, wait, we'll be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he drives his jeep and we drive over to this-- to this buil-- set of buildings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was about three buildings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and one of them has a sign in German that says-- and there's a picture of it in there-- that says Bad, which is bath I guess.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's also a warning sign, the international sign for death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, this is the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And OK, so we went in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
